    dc:description "Figure 17. Squamata indet. from the Echzell locality. Premaxilla HLMD-Ez 1989 in (A) anterior, (B) posterior, and (C) lateral views. Right quadrate HLMD-Ez 2002 in (D) lateral, and (E) medial views. Left pterygoid HLMD-Ez 2003 in (F) dorsal and (G) ventral views. Osteoderms HLMD-Ez 2000 (H-J) and 2001 (K-M) in (H, K) external, (I, L) internal and (J, M) posterior views." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/682237" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

